Package: scoutbaR
Title: Scoutbar 'React' Widget for 'shiny'
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("David", "Granjon", , "david@cynkra.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Creates a contextual menu that can be triggered with keyboard shortcuts or programmatically.
    Leverages the scoutbar 'React' API at <https://www.scoutbar.co/>. This can replace traditional
    sidebar or navigation bars, thereby enhancing the user experience with lighter user interfaces.
